headline.main: Chinese Cities Pressured by Home Prices Need to Boost Land Supply-PM
headline.print_headline: Chinese Cities Pressured by Home Prices Need to Boost Land Supply-PM

lead_paragraph: Chinese cities under pressure from soaring home prices need to boost land supply appropriately while authorities take measures to fight an inventory overhang in smaller cities, Premier Li Keqiang said on Sunday.
